            <p>
	<strong>Afghanistan</strong></p>
<p>
	<span style="font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;">Secretariat of Independent Administrative reform &amp; Civil Service Commission</span></p>
<p>
	<span style="font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;">Kabul</span></p>
